Olarrabal le Abija o Yeroboam

(
1   Ilai 
15  .
1  -
8  )


1  Ore to lari le tomon o isiet le nkitoria o laiguanani Yeroboam, neiteru Abija aitoreisho te Yuda. 
2  Eitoreishe ninye ilarin okuni te Yerusalem. Ore apa enkarna e ng'otonye naa Mikaia, entito e Uriel le Gibea.

Netii apa olarrabal erishata e Abija o Yeroboam. 
3  Neipang Abija alo olarrabal eeta enjore oo ltung'ana yiolot to larrabal, iltung'ana nkalifuni iip ong'uan oogeluno. Neitoloku Yeroboam iltung'ana lenyena to larrabal aitoluaaki ninye, naa iltung'ana nkalifuni iip isiet magil, gelunot. 
4  Neitashe Abija tenchumata oldoinyio le Semaraim otii ina kop oo ldoinyio e Efraim, nejo, “Entoning'oki nanu, iyie Yeroboam o Israel pooki! 
5  Aimeishiaakino teneyiolou nchere, eishoo o Laitoriani Enkai oo Siraeli, enkitoria oo Siraeli pooki Daudi ntarasi to lmumai le munyan? 
6  Ore Yeroboam olayioni le Nebat ilo sinka le Solomon olayioni le Daudi, nedumunye agilunore olkitok lenye. 
7  Ore ilkulikae tung'ana le pesho, nerrumoki ninche Rehoboam olayioni le Solomon, ilo leton aa oti nemeeta enkarriyiano, metaasa enkarruoisho. Nemeidimaa apa Rehoboam ninche.


8  “Amaa taata, ijo iyie indim aitasheikinore enkitoria o Laitoriani too Nkaik oo layiok le Daudi, eji enkaraki nira iyie olorora, kitok, niata nkitanyaanyukot e Nkai oo lasho le sahabu, apa naaitobira Yeroboam aitaa nkaitin. 
9  Keitu iyie iaraa aipang'ie ilapolosak lo Laitoriani, ilayiok le Aron, o Lawi, nintobiraki kewan ilapolosak anaa iltung'ana le kulie kuapi? Ore pooki ng'ae olotu aitisiny kewan to loti oing'oni anaa too lmeregeshi oopishana neaku olapolosani le nena neme Nkaitin. 
10  Kake ore tialo iyiook, Olaitoriani ninye Enkai ang, neitu iyiook kipuo aaing'ua ninye. Kiata iyiook ilapolosak ooisiaaita Olaitoriani laa ilayiok le Aron, o Lawi te nkaraki enkisiaayiare enye. 
11  Kepolosaki ninche Olaitoriani anaake tadekenya o teipa ilasarri oopejori, o enkorropil o sonkoyoni naarropil, neirragie emukate e nkitoduaaroto te mesa e sahabu nasila, neing'or nena kitasheta oo ltaai e sahabu pee etum iltaai lenyena aayupuyupo anaake teipa. Amu eikimbung iyiook enkitanapata Olaitoriani Enkai ang, kake itanyaita intae ninye. 
12  Ng'ura etii Enkai tenebo iyiook, ninye orikito iyiook, tenebo ilapolosak eeta ntarumpetani enye o larrabal pee eosh tenikinteru olarrabal o intae. Nakera, e Israel emiarare intae Olaitoriani Enkai oo loo minyi, amu mimirishosho.


13  Neirriu apa Yeroboam iltung'ana olnukata aitaman ninche te siadi. Netii ilturrurri lenyena dukuya iltung'ana le Yuda. Netii lelo tung'ana oonuka siadi ninche. 
14  Ore pee eing'orisho Yuda, ng'ura etii olarrabal dukuya o siadi, neishiraki ninche Olaitoriani nekut ilapolosak ntarumpetani. 
15  Neitayu iltung'ana le Yuda embuakunoto o larrabal. Ore ake pee ebuaku iltung'ana le Yuda nemir Enkai Yeroboam o Siraeli pooki ootii dukuya Abija o Yuda. 
16  Neilanyisho iltung'ana loo Siraeli te dukuya iltung'ana le Yuda neishoru Enkai ninche apik atua Nkaik e Yuda. 
17  Nesesekuan Abija o ltung'ana lenyena iltung'ana kumok oleng; neaku etuata too Siraeli iltung'ana gelunot nkalifuni iip imiet. 
18  Neaku eidimuaki apa iltung'ana loo Siraeli ina kata, neisulu iltung'ana le Yuda, enkaraki naigarakinote ninche Olaitoriani, Enkai oo loo menye. 
19  Nesujaa Abija Yeroboam, neoru ninye nkanas, Betel o nkang'itie enyena kutiti o Yeshana tenebo nkang'itie enyena kutiti o Efron tenebo nkang'itie enyena kutiti. 
20  Neitu aekata eitoki Yeroboam arrinyu engolon enye too nkolong'i e Abija. Neosh Olaitoriani ninye neye ninye. 
21  Kake etaa Abija magilani, neyam ninye nkituaak tomon oo ng'uan, netum ilayiok tikitam oare, o ntoyie tomon o ile. 
22  Ore nkulie kiaasin pooki e Abija, nkoitoi enyena o nkirorot enyena, neigeroki too nkatinin o loiboni le Nkai oji Ido.

